            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the roasted veg is done, heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>roasted veg</strong> with the<strong> teriyaki sauce</strong> to the pan and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Cook for 2-3 min or until the sauce has reduced to a sticky consistency – this is your <strong>aubergine & Tenderstem teriyaki</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1650363024034-x200.jpg",
