            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s] </strong>finely</p><p>Remove the <strong>aubergine & Tenderstem teriyaki </strong>from the heat and add your <strong>toasted sesame seeds</strong> to the pan</p>",
      "order": 7,
