      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>aubergine & Tenderstem teriyaki</strong> over the <strong>cooked rice </strong>and<strong> peas</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
